  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Cereals Value Chains Enhancement Project</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This is a following on project from the Kenya SALI ITL project, although is actually separate from ITL itself. The project will take place in Kenya and focus on increasing the income of 4,000 small scale and marginalized farmers and develop sustainable climate-resilient livelihoods, supporting micro-enterprises capacity to engage in the value chain as service providers and  creating a fair and sustainable sorghum and greengams value chain.</narrative>
  </description>
